<br><br><hr><a name=850><br>850</a><p> auchmeros {owkh-may-ros'}
from auchmos [probably from a base akin to that of 109] (dust, as dried by wind) ; adj

 AV - dark 1; 1

 1) squalid, dirty
    1a) since dirty things are destitute of brightness: dark


