<br><br><hr><a name=891><br>891</a><p> achri {akh'-ree} or achris {akh'-rece}
akin to <a href="200.html#206"<br>206</a> (through the idea of a terminus) ; prep/conj

 AV - until 14, unto 13, till 3, till + 3739 + 302 3, until + 3739 2,
      while + 3739 2, even to 2, misc 7; 49

 1) until, unto, etc.


