from the same as <a href="900.html#901"<br>901</a>; TDNT - 1:517,89; n n

 AV - depth 5, deep 1, deep + 2596 1, deepness 1, deep thing 1; 9

 1) depth, height
    1a) of "the deep" sea
    1b) metaph.
        1b1) deep, extreme, poverty
        1b2) of the deep things of God


