from <a href="550.html#575"<br>575</a> and the base of <a href="3550.html#3551"<br>3551</a>; v

 AV - give 1; 1

 1) to assign, portion out


<a href="#home"><img src="../pic/top.jpg" border=0></a>&nbsp&nbsp<a href="../index.html"><img src="../pic/hom.jpg" border=0></a>
<br><br><hr><a name=633><br>633</a><p> aponipto {ap-on-ip'-to}
from <a href="550.html#575"<br>575</a> and <a href="3500.html#3538"<br>3538</a>; v

 AV - wash 1; 1

 1) to wash off
 1) to wash off one's self, to wash off for one's self


<a href="#home"><img src="../pic/top.jpg" border=0></a>&nbsp&nbsp<a href="../index.html"><img src="../pic/hom.jpg" border=0></a>
