<br><br><hr><a name=635><br>635</a><p> apoplanao {ap-op-lan-ah'-o}
from <a href="550.html#575"<br>575</a> and <a href="4100.html#4105"<br>4105</a>; TDNT - 6:228,857; v

 AV - seduce 1, err 1; 2

 1) to cause to go astray
 2) to lead away from the truth to error
 3) to go astray, stray away from


