<br><br><hr><a name=638><br>638</a><p> apopnigo {ap-op-nee'-go}
from <a href="550.html#575"<br>575</a> and <a href="4150.html#4155"<br>4155</a>; TDNT - 6:455,895; v

 AV - choke 3; 3

 1) to choke
    1a) to suffocate with water, drown


<a href="#home"><img src="../pic/top.jpg" border=0></a>&nbsp&nbsp<a href="../index.html"><img src="../pic/hom.jpg" border=0></a>
<br><br><hr><a name=639><br>639</a><p> aporeo {ap-or-eh'-o}
from a compound of <a href="0.html#1"<br>1</a> (as a negative particle) and the base of <a href="4150.html#4198"<br>4198</a>; v

 AV - doubt 2, be perplexed 1, stand in doubt 1; 4

 1) to be without resources, to be in straits, to be left wanting,
    to be embarrassed, to be in doubt, not to know which way to turn
 2) to be at a loss with one's self, be in doubt
 3) not to know how to decide or what to do, to be perplexed


<a href="#home"><img src="../pic/top.jpg" border=0></a>&nbsp&nbsp<a href="../index.html"><img src="../pic/hom.jpg" border=0></a>
