    1a) of sailors lightening ship during a storm to avoid shipwreck


<a href="#home"><img src="../pic/top.jpg" border=0></a>&nbsp&nbsp<a href="../index.html"><img src="../pic/hom.jpg" border=0></a>
<br><br><hr><a name=671><br>671</a><p> apochresis {ap-okh'-ray-sis}
from a compound of <a href="550.html#575"<br>575</a> and <a href="5500.html#5530"<br>5530</a>; n f

 AV - using 1; 1

 1) abuse, misuse


