 ++++
 Used in Greek society of those who did not show up for work.


<a href="#home"><img src="../pic/top.jpg" border=0></a>&nbsp&nbsp<a href="../index.html"><img src="../pic/hom.jpg" border=0></a>
<br><br><hr><a name=814><br>814</a><p> ataktos {at-ak'-toce}
from <a href="800.html#813"<br>813</a>; TDNT - 8:47,1156; adv

 AV - disorderly 2; 2

 1) disorderly, out of ranks (often so of soldiers)
 2) irregular, inordinate, immoderate pleasures
 3) deviating from the prescribed order or rule


<a href="#home"><img src="../pic/top.jpg" border=0></a>&nbsp&nbsp<a href="../index.html"><img src="../pic/hom.jpg" border=0></a>
