<DOCHDR>
http://www.bju.edu:80/resources/teen/story.html 198.69.96.10 19970118034323 text/html 7815
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.12
Date: Saturday, 18-Jan-97 02:42:09 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 19-Aug-96 20:35:59 GMT
Content-length: 7624
