<HEAD><TITLE>Eternal Life</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">

<center><H3>I believe in<BR>
the gift of eternal life by the grace of God
</H3></center>
<img src="/graphics/horiz.gif">

<DL>
<DT><B>Salvation is a gift, by grace (i.e., without our merit).</B>

<DD><P><I>For by grace are ye saved through faith; and that not of
yourselves: [it is] the gift of God: Not of works, lest any
man should boast.</I> (Ephesians 2:8-9)

<P><I>For the wages of sin [is] death; but the gift of God [is]
eternal life through Jesus Christ our Lord.</I> (Romans 6:23)

<DT><HR><B>It comes to those who believe on Christ.</B>

<DD><P><I>And this is life eternal, that they might know thee the only
true God, and Jesus Christ, whom thou hast sent.</I> (John 17:3)

<P><I>He that believeth on the Son hath everlasting life: and he that
believeth not the Son shall not see life; but the wrath of God
abideth on him.</I> (John 3:36)
</DL>

