<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>Virgin Birth</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">

<center><H3>I believe in<BR>
the virgin birth of our Lord and Savior, Jesus Christ
</H3>
</center>
<img src="/graphics/horiz.gif">

<DL>
<DT><P><B>Jesus Christ was born to a virgin.</B>

<DD><P><I>And I will put enmity between thee and the woman, and between
thy seed and her seed; it shall bruise thy head, and thou shalt
bruise his heel.</I> (Genesis 3:15)

<P><I>Therefore the Lord himself shall give you a sign; Behold, a
virgin shall conceive, and bear a son, and shall call his name
Immanuel.</I> (Isaiah 7:14)

<P><I>Behold, a virgin </I>[Gk. <I>parthenos</I>, unambiguous
``virgin'']<I> shall be with child, and shall bring forth a
son, and they shall call his name Emmanuel, which being
interpreted is, God with us.</I> <a href="/bible/mt/1.html#23">(Matthew 1:23)</a>

<P><I>And Jacob begat Joseph the husband of Mary, of whom was born
Jesus, who is called Christ.</I> <a href="/bible/mt/1.html#16">(Matthew 1:16)</a>

<P><I>But when the fulness of the time was come, God sent forth his
Son, made of a woman, made under the law.</I> <a href="/bible/ga/4.html#4">(Galatians 4:4)</a>

<DT><HR><B>The virgin birth provided full humanity to Christ without
passing on the sin of Adam.</B>

<DD><P><I>For as in Adam all die, even so in Christ shall all be made
alive.</I> <a href="/bible/1co/15.html#22">(1 Corinthians 15:22)</a>

<DT><HR><B>The miracle of sinless birth occurred in the birth of
Christ, not in the birth of His mother.</B>

<DD><P><I>For all have sinned, and come short of the glory of God.</I>
<a href="/bible/rm/3.html#23">(Romans 3:23)</a>

<P><I>And my spirit hath rejoiced in God my Saviour.</I> <a href="/bible/lk/1.html#47">(Luke 1:47)</a>
</DL>

<HR>
<center>
<a href="05identi.html">Next Page</a> | <a href="03incarn.html">Previous Page</a> | <a href="index.html">First Page</a>
</center>
</BODY>
</HTML>
