<DOCNO>WT24-B08-82</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA043-000789-B027-426</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.bju.edu:80/resources/viewpoint/critic.html 198.69.96.10 19970118034217 text/html 2862
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.12
Date: Saturday, 18-Jan-97 02:41:06 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 19-Aug-96 20:36:08 GMT
