<DOCOLDNO>IA043-000789-B021-102</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.bju.edu:80/press/resource/tips/23feb94.html 198.69.96.10 19970118031113 text/html 7992
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.12
