<DOCHDR>
http://www.bju.edu:80/press/resource/tips/21nov91.html 198.69.96.10 19970118030957 text/html 7299
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.12
Date: Saturday, 18-Jan-97 02:08:35 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 29-Nov-96 19:32:38 GMT
Content-length: 7108
