<h2><IMG SRC="greendot.gif" Height=14 Width=15 ALT=" ">
<FONT face="Rockwell, Comic Sans MS, Arial">
What&#0146;s New in Diabetes:</font></h2>
<UL COMPACT TYPE=square>

<li>
The JDF has issued a
<em><a href="jdf-a-09.htm">Government Relations Legislative Alert</a></em>
<nobr>[Feb 04]</nobr>
<li><em><a href="rezulin.htm">Troglitazone</a></em> has been approved by the US FDA
<nobr>[updated Feb 14]</nobr>
</ul>

<h2><IMG SRC="greendot.gif" Height=14 Width=15 ALT=" ">
<FONT face="Rockwell, Comic Sans MS, Arial">
What&#0146;s New in Cyberspace:</font></h2>
<UL COMPACT TYPE=square>

<li>The 
<STRONG><font size="+2" color="#ff00cc">D</font><font color="#ff00cc">IABETES</font>
<font size="+2" color="#ff00cc">M</font><font color="#ff00cc">ONITOR</font></STRONG>
is please to publish information about
<em><a href="ny.htm">Coverage under New York's Diabetes Insurance Mandate</a></em>
<nobr>[Feb 15]</nobr>


<li>
Information about lispro insulin (Humalog&reg;) may now be found at
Eli Lilly's website, <em><a href="http://www.lilly.com/diabetes/humalog/index.html">
Managing your Diabetes</a></em>
<nobr>[Feb 12]</nobr>
</ul>

<h2><IMG SRC="greendot.gif" Height=14 Width=15 ALT=" ">
<FONT face="Rockwell, Comic Sans MS, Arial">
