<blockquote><P><H2>
You may search
DIABETES MONITOR,
children with DIABETES,
the Juvenile Diabetes Foundation,
or all three
websites using one or more keywords.
</h2>
<P>
Please note: The <STRONG>
<font size="+2" color="#ff00cc">D</font><font color="#ff00cc">IABETES</font>
<font size="+2" color="#ff00cc">M</font><font color="#ff00cc">ONITOR</font></STRONG>
now has an <em><a href="dm-index.htm">index.</a></em> If you are searching for a word or concept at this website,
and wish it were in the index, please <em><A HREF="mailto:monitor@mdcc.com">
send an e-mail</a></em> and we&#0146;ll put the word into the index!
<P>
