<center><H2>
<FONT SIZE="+3">I</font>nformation and <FONT SIZE="+3">S</font>ervices
</h2></center>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<IMG SRC="mdcc1414.gif" ALT=" " height=14 width=14>
<A HREF="mdccinfo.htm"><EM>Information about the MDCC</EM></A>
(Hours,
Telephone Calls,
Our Medical Staff,
New Patients,
Appointments,
Non-Smoking Policy,
Emergency Care,
Appointments,
Diabetes Supplies,
Hospital Care,
Laboratory Tests,
How You Can Help)
<P>
<IMG SRC="mdcc1414.gif" ALT=" " Height=14 width=14>
<em><A HREF="dm-vip.htm">Very Intensive diabetes treatment Programs</em></A></em>
Using frequent blood sugar monitoring,
it is now possible for people with diabetes to
adjust their diabetes program themselves to match their lifestyles
<P>
<IMG SRC="mdcc1414.gif" ALT=" " Height=14 width=14>
<em><A HREF="pumps.htm">Using an insulin pump as part of the treatment of diabetes
</a></em>
<p>
