<A NAME="aadenews"></A><P>
<u><strong>AADE News</strong></u></em>
<br>
The newsletter of the <em><a href="http://www.aadenet.org">American Association of Diabetes Educators.</a></em>
Published bimonthly.
Active (and other) members of AADE receive a subscription as a membership benefit.
444 N Michigan Avenue, Suite 1240, Chicago IL 60611-3901.
<b><nobr>Target Audience:</b></nobr> Diabetes Educators.
<P>
Lead Article for
Volume 22, Number 9,
November/December 1996:
&#0147;Emergence of Managed Care: Major Trends&#0148;
