<blockquote><P><blockquote><P><center><h3>
These vendors supply sugarfree products.<br>
(Reminder: Sugarfree doesn&#0146;t mean caloriefree!)
<P>
Listed Alphabetically.
</h3></center></blockquote></blockquote>
<p><center>
<IMG SRC="red-line.gif" Height=2 Width=50% ALT=" ">
</center>

<a name="1sss"></a>
<h3>1-Stop Sugarless Shop</h3>
800-898-7571, or Fax 410-817-4636 or Email us at
<em><A HREF="mailto:SUGARLES@erols.com">SUGARLES@erols.com</A></em>
to get
your free catalog of the over 700 SUGARLESS PRODUCTS we have to offer at
reasonable prices. Baked goods, Baking products, Dessert Mixes, Drink 
Mixes, Cookies, Hard/Soft Candies, Chocolates, Sauces, and Spreads.  Our 
catalog contains necessary NUTRITION FACTS so that you can make a wise 
food choice to fit your diet plan.  We understand your needs as we are a 
family run business with a diabetic child.
<h3>Bitterman Family Confections</h3>
1-800-53-CANDY, or 1-816-221-2922. 1625 Oak St, Kansas City, MO 64108-1457. Catalog available.
<h3>Delty, Inc</h3>
1-800-962-3355. 7924 Ronson Road, #K, San Diego, CA 92111. Chocolates, peanut brittle, hard candy, caramel corn, gummibears, taffy, peppermint balls and fruit sticks, cookies, fudgesauce, syrups, holiday-specific molded chocolates, truffles, chocolate-covered cherries. Mail-order catalogs available.
<h3>Estee Corporation</h3>
1-800-526-5051. 169 Lackawanna Ave, Parsippany, NJ 07054-1094. Chocolates, hard candy, gumdrops, gummibears, cake mixes, preserves, syrups, gelatins, salad dressings. Widely available in supermarkets.
<h3>Featherweight Sweet Pretenders</h3>
Located in the diet section of grocery stores. For more information contact Featherweight Professional Program, P.O. Box 370, Minneapolis, MN 55440.
<h3>Mister Bulky</h3>
1-816-966-1221 (Bannister Mall, Kansas City, MO), 1-913-492-3231 (Oak Park Mall, Overland Park, KS) and 1-816-523-9191 (Ward Parkway Mall, Kansas City, MO). Wide variety of sugar-free chocolates and hard candies.
<h3>ND Labs, Inc</h3>
1-718-646-7998. 337 Shore Parkway, Brooklyn, NY 11235. Lollipops with HSH &#0147;Polypops&#0148; or &#0147;Healthpops&#0148; (the latter also removes artificial colors and flavors).
<h3>Prices Chocolates</h3>
1-816-561-8141. Located in Seville Square, at the Plaza, KANSAS CITY, MO. Wide range of sugar-free chocolates.

<h3>Simply Sugarfree</h3>
Allen Wertz, National Confectionery Brands, Inc, San Dimas, CA 91773.

<a name="sfce"></a>
<h3><em>
<a href="http://www.sugarfreecandy.com">Sugarfree Candy Express</a></em></h3>
Selling exclusively sugarfree candy
products.
We would be glad to offer a
discount to those who mention that they heard of us through the
Diabetes Monitor.
<h3>Sugarfree Center</h3>
800-972-2323. P.O. Box 114, Van Nuys, CA 91408. Provides diabetes supplies and equipment and gourmet health food. Mail-order catalog available.
<a name="sfmplace"></a>
<h3><em>
<IMG SRC="new3.gif" ALT=" New! ">
<a href="http://www.icanect.net/sugarfree">
Sugar Free Marketplace</a></em></h3>
&#0147;The Supermarket for the Diabetic.
All products we offer are without refined sugar, corn syrup, honey or molasses. Many items
are low sodium or sodium free. We recommend consulting your physician or diabetes
educator, as he or she is always your best source for advice concerning specific foods in your
food plan.&#0148;
Your satisfaction is guaranteed or your money back. 
Sugar Free Marketplace:
6710 N. University Drive,
Tamarac, Florida 33321;
telephone (954) 726-9747 or 1-800-726-6191;
fax (954) 726-9705;
E-mail: 
<em><A HREF="mailto:sugrfree@icanect.net">sugrfree@icanect.net</A></em>

<h3>The Diet Shoppe</h3>
1-708-679-5409. P.O. Box 1037, Evanston, IL 60204. Chocolates, hard candy, taffy, plus pudding, gelatin, beverages, cake mixes, cranberry sauce, jelly.

