<IMG SRC="star.gif" height=14 width=14 alt=" ">
<A HREF="http://www.minimed.com/index.htm">
<EM>MiniMed Web</EM>
</A> (&quot;http://www.minimed.com/index.htm&quot;)
<br>Information about insulin pumps from one of the major manufacturers.
<br><IMG SRC="star.gif" height=14 width=14 alt=" ">
<A HREF="http://www.diabetesnet.com/index.html">
<EM> The Diabetes Mall On the Net </EM>
</a>
(&quot;http://www.diabetesnet.com/index.html&quot;)
<br>
&quot;The Net's Resource For People With Diabetes
'Better health with diabetes through information.'
And products created through involvement.
Most products available from the Diabetes Mall are created and sold by people with diabetes.&quot;
<br><IMG SRC="star.gif" height=14 width=14 alt=" ">
<a href="http://www.iquest.net/sugarbusters/sugarbusters.html">
<EM>SugarBUSTERS Diabetes Supply Center</EM>
</a>
(&quot;http://www.iquest.net/sugarbusters/sugarbusters.html&quot;)
<br>A &quot;one-stop source for
your diabetes supplies.&quot;
<br><IMG SRC="star.gif" height=14 width=14 alt=" ">
<a href="http://maingate.net/mall/hpncos/wright.html">
<EM>The Wright Prefilled Syringe Case</EM>
</a>
(&quot;http://maingate.net/mall/hpncos/wright.html&quot;)
<br>A product for people on the go.
<br><IMG SRC="star.gif" height=14 width=14 alt=" ">
<a href="http://www.oxystat.com/diabetes">
<EM>Oxystat Home Health Care Systems</EM>
</a>
(&quot;http://www.oxystat.com/diabetes&quot;)
<br>&quot;A supermarket of supplies and
accessories for the patient with diabetes.&quot;
<br><IMG SRC="star.gif" height=14 width=14 alt=" ">
<a href="http://www.lilly.com">
<EM> Eli Lilly and Company</EM>
</a>
(&quot;http://www.lilly.com&quot;)
<br>
See below for Lilly's
<a href="other-03.htm#mgngdm">
<em>Managing Your Diabetes</a></em> website.

<br><IMG SRC="star.gif" height=14 width=14 alt=" ">
<A HREF="http://www.napplisci.com/welcome.html">
<EM> National Applied Science </EM>
</A>
(&quot;http://www.napplisci.com/welcome.html&quot;)
<br>A company specializing in implantable biosensor devices. This website
includes <A HREF="http://www.napplisci.com/diabhist.html">
<EM> A Short History of the Discovery and Treatment of Diabetes </EM>
</A>
(&quot;http://www.napplisci.com/diabhist.html&quot;)
and <A HREF="http://www.napplisci.com/diabinfo.html">
<EM> Background Information [about] Diabetes Mellitus
</EM></A>
(&quot;http://www.napplisci.com/diabinfo.html&quot;)
<br><IMG SRC="star.gif" height=14 width=14 alt=" ">
<A HREF="http://www.novo.dk">
<EM>
Novo Nordisk
</EM></A>
(&quot;http://www.novo.dk&quot;)
<br>Novo Nordisk's website no longer includes the beautiful drawings
of insulin and proinsulin molecules. There is a page entitled
<em><a href="http://www.novo.dk/backgrou/backgrou/badia1uk.htm">
Facts about diabetes.</a></em>
This website is in Denmark.
<br><IMG SRC="star.gif" height=14 width=14 alt=" ">
<a href="http://www.inetbiz.com/h-wave/">
<EM>Electronic Waveform Lab
</EM></a>
(&quot;http://www.inetbiz.com/h-wave/&quot;)
<br>This company promotes using &quotH-Wave Therapy&quot
in the treatment of
<a href="http://www.inetbiz.com/h-wave/background.html">
painful diabetic neuropathy
</EM></a>
(&quot;http://www.inetbiz.com/h-wave/background.html&quot;)
<br><IMG SRC="star.gif" height=14 width=14 alt=" ">
<a href="http://www.cybergate.net/~cjmele/">
<EM>Preferred Rx</EM></a>
(&quot;http://www.cybergate.net/~cjmele/&quot;)
You can mail-order prescription drugs, whether or not you have insurance.
Nothing specific mentioned about diabetes, though you can call their 800 number
for more information.
<br><IMG SRC="star.gif" height=14 width=14 alt=" ">
<EM><A HREF="http://www.infi.net/ndp/">
National Diabetic Pharmacies</a></EM>
(&quot;http://www.infi.net/ndp/&quot;)
