<br>
&#0147;Vigora Inc. is dedicated to making the control of diabetes easier. The company was founded and is operated by people with diabetes
or who are directly involved with the disease. The company conducts research into computerization of the control and maintenance
activities of people with diabetes. Vigora's objective is to eventually make control entirely computerized, safe, portable, and with
exciting and fun interfaces.&#0148;
