(&quot;http://www.mediject.com/&quot;)
&#0147;Creating The Standard for Needle-Free Drug Delivery.
Medi-Ject Corporation is the world leader in needle-free drug delivery systems. The core product for Medi-Ject is the Medi-Jector, a precision
medical instrument that delivers injectable drugs without the use of a needle. Currently used worldwide by persons with diabetes to deliver virtually
painless doses of insulin, Medi-Ject Corporation has also entered into arrangements with other injectable drug producers to bring this exciting
technology to even more consumers.&#0148;
