&#0147;The DiabetesDek is a pocket-sized reference 
tool that serves as a day-to-day guide for diabetes management.
Topics include what diabetes is, the basic types of diabetes, checking
your blood glucose, diabetes management, insulin, oral diabetes
medicines, meal planning, exercise, sick day guidelines, hypoglycemia,
hyperglycemia,tips for traveling, long-term concerns and how to get the
