SpectRx Inc.</a></em>
(&quot;http://www.spectrx.com&quot;)
&#0147;SpectRx, Inc. is a medical technology development company that
specializes in minimally
and non-invasive diagnostic and monitoring systems. Programs currently
under development
by SpectRx are a painless, bloodless personal glucose monitor, a
non-invasive bilirubin
testing device and a non-invasive diabetes screening device. SpectRx
controls 30 granted
or pending patents related to minimally and non-invasive medical
technology and more
sensitive, point-of-care invasive diagnostic tests using fluorescence
lifetime spectroscopy. The company has research and development arrangements with
15 universities, research institutions and hospitals worldwide.&#0148;
