<a name="dinit"></a><br>
<IMG SRC="new3.gif" ALT=" New! ">
<IMG SRC="star.gif" height=14 width=14 alt=" ">
<em><a href="http://www.musc.edu/diabetes/">Diabetes Initiative</a></em>
&quot;http://www.musc.edu/diabetes/&quot;
&#0147;The purpose of the Diabetes Initiative is to develop and implement a comprehensive statewide plan of community outreach
programs, health professional education, and diabetes surveillance. The goal is to provide the tools for management of the
disease in order to reduce severe complications and cost burdens for South Carolinians who suffer from diabetes mellitus.&#0148;

