<a name="lists"></a>
<img src="mdcc1414.gif"  Alt=" " height=14 width=14>
<A HREF="other-ds.htm">
<EM><strong><FONT SIZE="+2">D</FONT></strong>iabetes on the <strong><font size="+2">W</font></strong>eb</EM></A>
</A> (&quot;http://www.mdcc.com/other-ds.htm.htm&quot;)
<br>
&#0147;A hodgepodge of hyperlinks to huge and humble homepages,
websites, and webpages that have information (sometimes very
useful, and sometimes not) about diabetes and related health issues&#0148;
<br>From the Midwest Diabetes Care Center
<br>
<img src="mdcc1414.gif"  Alt=" " height=14 width=14>
<A HREF="dr-00001.htm">
<EM><strong><FONT SIZE="+2">D</FONT></strong>IABETES <strong><font size="+2">R</font></strong>EGISTRY</EM></A>
</A> (&quot;http://www.mdcc.com/dr-00001.htm&quot;)
<br>
&#0147;A wide-ranging list of webpages about
various aspects of diabetes care,
subdivided by topic&#0148;
<br>From the Midwest Diabetes Care Center
<a name="olrd"></a>
<br>
<IMG SRC="star.gif" height=14 width=14 alt=" ">
<A HREF="http://www.cruzio.com/~mendosa/faq.html">
<EM> On-Line Resources for Diabetics </EM>
</A>
(&quot;http://www.cruzio.com/~mendosa/faq.html&quot;)
<br>Compiled by Rick Mendosa
(Also available at the 
<strong><font size="+2" color="#ff00cc">D</font><font color="#ff00cc">IABETES</font>
<nobr><font size="+2" color="#ff00cc">M</font><font color="#ff00cc">ONITOR</font></STRONG>,</nobr>
at <nobr><em><a href="faq.htm">http://www.mdcc.com/faq.htm</a></em>)</nobr>
