<EM><a href="http://yahoo.com/Health/Diseases_and_Conditions/Diabetes">
Yahoo: diabetes
</a></EM>
(&quot;http://yahoo.com/Health/Diseases_and_Conditions/Diabetes&quot;)
<a name="ama_01"></a>
<br>
<IMG SRC="star.gif" height=14 width=14 alt=" ">
<A HREF="http://www.ama-assn.org/cgi-bin/search"><em>Search in medical journals</em></a>
published by the
<A HREF="http://www.ama-assn.org/"><em>American Medical Association</em></A>
on line.
(&quot;http://www.ama-assn.org/cgi-bin/search&quot;)
<br>
(First, set up a free password, which is available by signing up at
<A HREF="http://www.ama-assn.org/register/register.htm">
<em>&quot;http://www.ama-assn.org/register/register.htm&quot;</em></a>).
<br>Searching for &quot;<strong>diabetes</strong>&quot; in &quot;<strong>all</strong>&quot; journals yielded 11 articles on January 26, 1996
<a name="jeans"></a>
