&#0147;This database provides titles, abstracts and availability information on diabetes information and health education materials.
The value of this database is that it lists a wealth of health promotion and education materials that are not indexed elsewhere. This is not a full-text
database because many of the materials are produced by organizations other than NIDDK or NIH--meaning many of the materials are copyrighted.&#0148;
From the National Institute of Diabetes and Digestive and Kidney Diseases (NIDDK) of the National Institutes of
Health (NIH).

