<a name="h-tea"></a>
<IMG SRC="star.gif" height=14 width=14 alt=" ">
<a href="http://www.diabetea.com">
<em>
Diabetes Herbal Treatment Home Page
</em></a>
(&quot;http://www.diabetea.com&quot;)
<br>
A promotion for Gymnema Herbal Tea from Malaysia. &#0147;In experimental and clinical trials, Gymnema sylvestre has been successful in treating both insulin dependent and
non-insulin dependent diabetes without reducing the blood sugar level to below the normal blood sugar levels, an
effect seen with the use of insulin or oral hypoglycemic sulphonylurea compounds.&#0148;
It also is touted for &#0147;Snakebite, Fever, and Swollen glands&#0148;
(when mixed with castor oil)!

