<a name="Feb97"></a><center><H3>February, 1997</H3></center>
<BLOCKQUOTE><p>
<strong>6)</strong>  &#0147;Wellness Through Self Care&#0148;	
ADA Heart of America Chapter Meeting (at Life Dynamics Building, Shawnee Mission, KS).
Call ADA office, (816) 361-3361
<br>

<strong>6, 11, 12, 17, 19, 27)</strong>  &#0147;Achieving Goals&#0148;	
ADA Metropolitan Patient Education meetings (at various locations in MO and KS).
Call ADA office, (816) 361-3361
<br>

<strong>10)</strong>
<em><a href="support.htm#JDFDSGSJHC">Adult Type I Support Group</a></EM> (at Saint Joseph Health Center)
Call JDF office, (913) 831-7997
<br>

</BLOCKQUOTE>

<a name="Mar97"></a><center><H3>March, 1997</H3></center>
<BLOCKQUOTE><p>
<strong>6)</strong>  &#0147;Neuropathies of Diabetes&#0148;	
ADA Heart of America Chapter Meeting (at Life Dynamics Building, Shawnee Mission, KS).
Call ADA office, (816) 361-3361
<br>

<strong>10)</strong>
<em><a href="support.htm#JDFDSGSJHC">Adult Type I Support Group</a></EM> (at Saint Joseph Health Center)
Call JDF office, (913) 831-7997
<br>

<strong>11)</strong>  &#0147;Carbohydrate Counting and New Resources&#0148;	
KCRADE Chapter Meeting (at Saint Joseph Health Center, Kansas City, MO)
Call Clark Johnson, RPh, CDE, Chapter President
at (816) 373-4415x1053
or E-mail to <em><A HREF="mailto:insula@sky.net">insula@sky.net</A></em>
<br>
</BLOCKQUOTE>

