ADA Heart of America Chapter Meeting (at Life Dynamics Building, Shawnee Mission, KS).
Call ADA office, (816) 361-3361
<br>

<strong>3, 8, 9, 16, 21, 19, 24)</strong>  &#0147;Travel with Diabetes&#0148;	
ADA Metropolitan Patient Education meetings (at various locations in MO and KS).
Call ADA office, (816) 361-3361
<br>

<strong>5)</strong>
David Koller Bullhead Fishing Classic, benefitting JDF-KCC
(at Moundridge, KS)
Call JDF office, (913) 831-7997
<br>

<strong>7-18)</strong> Diabetes Education Update.
An Intensive Workshop and Practicum for nurses and dietitians. (Wichita, KS)
Call Wichita State University, at (316) 689-3731.
<BR>

<strong>26)</strong>
Third Annual Celebrity Monopoly Tournament and Gala
(at the Ritz-Carlton Hotel, Kansas City, MO)
Call JDF office, (913) 831-7997
<br>

</BLOCKQUOTE>

