(&quot;http://rampages.onramp.net/~drjim/&quot;)
<br>
Dr. Jim offers answers to a few common dog and cat problems;
no diabetes mentioned when reviewed on July 14, 1996. <strong>Site unavailable when attempted November 15, 1996</strong>
<br>
