<title>Diabetes Monitor - Easter Egg Hunt</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<body BGCOLOR="#DFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" ALINK="#0000FF" background="bd2.gif" VLINK="#FF0000">
<a name="top"></a><a name="_top"></a>
<table>
<td>
<IMG src="spinstar.gif" height=47 width=47 ALT=" " align=left>
</td><td>
<h2><strong>
<font SIZE="+3"><A HREF="index.htm" TARGET="_top">D</a></FONT><font color="#ff00cc">IABETES</font>
<FONT SIZE="+3"><a href="with.htm" TARGET="_top">M</a></FONT><font color="#ff00cc">ONITOR:</font>
<br>
<FONT face="Rockwell, Comic Sans MS, Arial">
Easter Egg Hunt!
</FONT>
</td><br>
</table>
<IMG SRC="red-line.gif" width=100% Height=2 ALT=" ">
</h2></strong>
<blockquote><P>
<IMG SRC="estregg2.gif" Height=171 Width=400 ALT=" Egg Picture " ALIGN="middle">
<P>The
<FONT SIZE="+1" color="#FF0000"><STRONG>D</STRONG></FONT><font color="#ff00cc">IABETES</font> <FONT SIZE="+1" color="#FF0000"><STRONG>M</STRONG></FONT><font color="#ff00cc">ONITOR</font>
</strong>
now has a hidden Easter Egg for you to find!
<P>
When you find the Easter Egg, you'll find an unexpected hyperlink to &quot;http://www.mdcc.com/e-egg.htm.&quot;
<br>
When you find this hyperlink, click on it and see what happens!
<h3>
The location of the Easter Egg will be changed from time to time.
</h3>
</center>
</h2>
<blockquote><P><blockquote><P>
The Easter Egg will be marked by a hyperlink called &quot;<strong>http://www.mdcc.com/e-egg.htm</strong>.&quot;
<P>Hyperlinks are frequently underlined, or a different color.
Here's an <strong>example of a hyperlink:</strong>
<A HREF="egg-info.htm"><STRONG><em>This is a HYPERLINK that does nothing</em></STRONG></a>.
The shape of the cursor arrow will change when you move your cursor
over the words &#147;This is a HYPERLINK that does nothing&#148; in the previous sentence.
Please also notice that the name of the linked file given in this example ends with &quot;egg-info.htm&quot;
(Since this is only an example, clicking on this hyperlink will only reload this page.)
</blockquote></blockquote>
</blockquote>

