<IMG SRC="1pix.gif" Height=1 Width=2 ALT=" ">
to see a listing
of the various sections of the 
<nobr><strong><font color="#ff00cc">DIABETES MONITOR</font></STRONG>.)</nobr>
</td></table>
<center><font size=-1>The URL for this webpage is 
http://www.mdcc.com/dm-fam-p.htm
</font>
<IMG SRC="1pix.gif" Height=1 Width=4 ALT=" ">
