<DOCNO>WT24-B08-227</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA006-000064-B024-209</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.mdcc.com:80/flexible.htm 206.112.197.145 19970221234403 text/html 11747
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 21 Feb 1997 23:47:17 GMT
