<h3>Typographical Errors</h3>
<UL COMPACT TYPE=square>
<li>Type <strong><font color="red">!</font></strong> Diabetes (Sometimes we all feel like we&#0146;re dealing with @#$%^&* diabetes!)
<li>Type <strong><font color="red">11</font></strong> diabetes (comes after Type 10?)
<li>One Tou<strong><font color="red">g</font></strong>h Meter (One really great idea)
<li>Gluco<strong><font color="red">n</font></strong>trol
(Sounds like a brand of pill to control blood sugar levels, but it&#0146;s got one too many letters)
<li>Stom<strong><font color="red">ache</font></strong>
(A smaller version of a bellyache?)
<li>A <strong><font color="red">cur</font></strong>
for diabetes (or perhaps a cat?)
<li>S<strong><font color="red">e</font></strong>rfing (the net...  Recognition that we all can become slaves to our addictions)
</ul>

