<title>Diabetes Monitor - Diabetes on the Web: Websites Multilinguisticos</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<body BGCOLOR="#DFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" ALINK="#0000FF" background="bd2.gif" VLINK="#FF0000">
<a name="top"></a><a name="_top"></a>
<table>
<td>
<IMG src="spinstar.gif" height=47 width=47 ALT=" " align=left>
</td><td>
<h2><strong>
<font SIZE="+3"><A HREF="index.htm" TARGET="_top">D</a></FONT><font color="#ff00cc">IABETES</font>
<FONT SIZE="+3"><a href="with.htm" TARGET="_top">M</a></FONT><font color="#ff00cc">ONITOR:</font>
<br>
<FONT face="Rockwell, Comic Sans MS, Arial">
<nobr>DIABETES on the WEB:</nobr><br>
Websites Multilinguisticos
</FONT>
</td><br>
</table>
<IMG SRC="red-line.gif" width=100% Height=2 ALT=" ">
</h2></strong>
<blockquote><P>
<font color="#ff00cc">
 . . . as of November 23, 1996
</font><P>
<center><IMG SRC="red-line.gif" ALT=" " Height=2 Width=50%><p>
<h2><em><a href="#dani">Danish</a></em>
 |  <em><a href="#dutc">Dutch/Nederlands</a></em>
 |  <em><a href="#fren">French/Franais</a></em>
 |  <em><a href="#germ">German/Deutsch</a></em>
 |  <em><a href="#norw">Norwegian</a></em>
 |  <em><a href="#port">Portuguese/Portugus</a></em>
 |  <em><a href="#span">Spanish/Espaol</a></em>
</h2>
<IMG SRC="red-line.gif" ALT=" " Height=2 Width=50%>
</center>
<blockquote><P>
Esto es  un esfuerzo peque&#0241;o para ayudar a gente con diabetes en todos partes
del mundo.  Si usted conoce otro &quot;websites&quot; sobre la diabetes en Espa&#241;ol (o
cualquier otro idioma) favor de notificarme por correo-e (e-mail) a:
<em><A HREF="mailto:monitor@mdcc.com">monitor@mdcc.com</A></em>
<P>
&#161;Si usted es biling&#252;e y quisiera ayudarme con traducciones, favor de notificarme!
</blockquote>
<blockquote><P><blockquote><P>
Muchas gracias a Tom&#0225;s Bartol, RN-CS, MN
(direccion de correo-e "e-mail":
<em><A HREF="mailto:BART111W@wonder.em.cdc.gov">BART111W@wonder.em.cdc.gov</A></em>)
por so ayuda en las traducciones.

</blockquote>
The following is a small attempt at helping people with diabetes from throughout the world.
If you  know of additional non-English language sites that are available for people interested in diabetes, please send e-mail to me at
<em><A HREF="mailto:monitor@mdcc.com">monitor@mdcc.com</A></em>
<P>
If you are are multilingual, in any language plus English, and would want to help with translations, please let me know!
</blockquote>
<blockquote><P><blockquote><P>
Thanks to Tom Bartol, RN-CS, MN
(e-mail address:
<em><A HREF="mailto:bart111w@wonder.em.cdc.gov">bart111w@wonder.em.cdc.gov</A></em>)
for his assistance in translations to and from Spanish.
</blockquote></blockquote>
<p><center>
<IMG SRC="red-line.gif" Height=2 Width=50% ALT=" ">
</center>
